snippet.title: U.S. Supreme Court Nominee Ketanji Brown Jackson can't define the word "WOMAN"!?
snippet.description:
Republican Senator Marsha Blackburn asks U.S. Supreme Court Nominee Ketanji Brown Jackson to provide a definition for the word "woman". SPOILER ALERT: She can't... and the discussion begins!

#SupremeCourt #KetanjiBrownJackson #Blackburn #DefineWoman
